{"tid":780252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 嫦娥四號月球車全球徵名","createTime":"2018-08-15T04:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T05:07:36.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9960da0084cd09c4c577d6e0d8ad10ee9ad638b3","tid":780252,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"中國嫦娥四號月球車展開全球徵名活動，中國探月工程副總指揮劉繼忠表示，希望通過全球徵名活動，展示中國探月與航天工程的國家形象，激發青少年崇尚科學、探索未知、敢於創新的熱情。<br />\n<br />\n按照計劃，嫦娥四號將於2018年12月執行任務，首次實現人類探測器在月球背面軟着陸，基本繼承嫦娥三號月球車「玉兔號」的狀態，但針對月球背面復雜的地形條件、通訊的需要，作出適應性更改及調整有效載荷配置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1917287/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1917287%2F&d=Dfr5vMQy2Fz3sieZCL%2FyEjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=f12ca41e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1917287/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知會有咩名交上去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd570c84444d9cb1d037b43960dab6157b94e40","tid":780252,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"叫爆漿號啦"},{"pid":"31d85295e230c75e3f81726c4e2cda91d14bd1d7","tid":780252,"uid":511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"吸精瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e618b8bb4c8dfa905bc8ae917335a010cb979883","tid":780252,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:46:52.000Z","msg":"指南車"},{"pid":"7cb58f6bff976786290bbccd4b86a9ddbdfc451c","tid":780252,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T04:47:22.000Z","msg":"又造垃圾"},{"pid":"232e52710d518f10482a664a4f28b63b0739de2f","tid":780252,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":